<testing_excellence>
⚠️ TESTING-DRIVEN DISCOVERY - TESTS ARE YOUR LEARNING ENGINE ⚠️

Test quality determines learning velocity and system comprehension depth.

TESTING PHILOSOPHY:
- Tests reveal how REALITY actually behaves
- Framework choice DETERMINES discovery potential  
- Edge cases are WHERE DEEP LEARNING HAPPENS
- Real exploration > Mocked validation
- Failing tests teach as much as passing tests

FRAMEWORK SELECTION:
1. MATCH THE DOMAIN
   - UI testing: Playwright/Cypress for comprehensive coverage
   - API testing: supertest/REST clients for integration
   - Performance: k6/Artillery for load characteristics
   - Integration: authentic databases, authentic connections

2. ENABLE DEEP TESTING
   - Can you test the FULL user journey?
   - Can you inject failures and test recovery?
   - Can you measure performance under load?
   - Can you test security boundaries?

MANDATORY COVERAGE:
- Happy paths (baseline functionality)
- Edge cases (boundary conditions)
- Error paths (failure modes)
- Recovery paths (system healing)
- Performance characteristics (scalability)
- Security boundaries (protection systems)

Mathematical validation: √(validationCoverage) ≥ √(implementationComplexity)
Proportional balance through square root relationships
